(G) a retirement benefit, including a disability insurance benefit and a dependent’s or survivor’s benefit under subchapter II of chapter 7 of title 42, awarded before September 26, 1961, to an individual or his survivor or beneficiary, insofar as the individual, before September 26, 1961—(i) was convicted of an offense named by subsection (c) of section 8312 of this title, to the extent provided by that subsection; or

